Class BinaryTree<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • BinaryTree<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Any class to hold in trees nodes.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinarySearchTree

    public class BinaryTree<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to hold given information of type E in a binary tree.
